Package net.objectzoo.ebc.split

This package contains EBCs that allow to split EBC flows.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SplitProcess<Parameter>
    The SplitProcess distributes the process and its parameter to multiple subscribers.
    SplitProcessToSignal<Parameter>
    The SplitProcessToSignal distributes the process and its parameter to multiple regular subscribers and to multiple signal subscribers.
    SplitSignal
    The SplitSignal distributes the signal to multiple subscribers.

Package net.objectzoo.ebc.split Description

This package contains EBCs that allow to split EBC flows.
